request.description:
Sends a notification to specified channels. Dispatches synchronously using the channel adapters.

Required fields: eventId, eventType, userId, channels (non-empty array), templateId.
Optional: payload (map of data for template rendering).

Valid EventTypes: ORDER_PLACED, ORDER_SHIPPED, ORDER_DELIVERED, PAYMENT_FAILED, PASSWORD_RESET, ACCOUNT_CREATED, USER_INVITED, PROMOTION_ALERT, FRAUD_ALERT, SYSTEM_ALERT

Valid Channels: EMAIL, SMS, PUSH, WEBHOOK

Response (200):
```json
{
  "eventId": "evt-001-20260617",
  "success": true,
  "status": "success",
  "message": "Notification sent successfully",
  "channelResults": {
    "EMAIL": {
      "success": true,
      "messageId": "sendgrid_mock_evt-001-20260617_email",
      "errorMessage": null
    },
    "SMS": {
      "success": true,
      "messageId": "twilio_mock_evt-001-20260617_sms",
      "errorMessage": null
    }
  }
}
```
